rt Hyperlink\"></w:LsdException>\n </w:LatentStyles>\n</xml><![endif]-->\n\n<!--[if gte mso 10]>\n<style>\n /* Style Definitions */\ntable.MsoNormalTable\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\n	mso-style-priority:99;\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n	font-size:12.0pt;\n	font-family:DengXian;\n	mso-ascii-font-family:DengXian;\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-fareast-font-family:DengXian;\n	mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\n	mso-hansi-font-family:DengXian;\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n\n\n\n<!--StartFragment-->\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1/PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">免疫疗法是当前备受瞩目的新一类抗癌免疫疗法，旨在利用人体自身的免疫系统抵御癌症。通过阻断</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1/PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">信号通路使癌细胞死亡，具有治疗多种类型肿瘤的潜力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">是一种主要表达于活化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">T</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">细胞上的抑制性受体，与其配体</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">结合，可显著抑制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">T</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">细胞的活化和增殖，并调节细胞因子的表达和分泌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">则广泛表达于多种免疫细胞、上皮细胞以及肿瘤细胞。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">肿瘤细胞通过高表达的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">分子，与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">T</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">细胞上的受体</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">结合，传递负调控信号，导致肿瘤抗原特异性</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">T</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">细胞的诱导凋亡和免疫无能，使肿瘤细胞逃避机体的免疫监控和杀伤。目前诸多研究表明，多种人类肿瘤大量表达的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">分子与患者临床病理特征及预后紧密相关，成为肿瘤检出和预后判断的新的生物学指标。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><img src=\"http://7xpsze.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/FiVVuEKgCj3-vVTMD5UMc0zUiu1i\" data-filename=\"FD-L.png\" style=\"width: 643px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: \'MS Mincho\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">国</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">际现</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: \'MS Mincho\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">状</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#444444;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2014</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">月，百时美公司的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">抑制剂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Opdivo</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Nivolumab</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">）在日本获批，是全球首个批准的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">抑制剂，现已在全球三大主要市场（美日欧）获批。该药适用于不能手术切除或转移性黑色素瘤，转移性非小细胞肺癌，以及晚期肾癌患者的治疗。默沙东公司的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Keytruda</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Pembrolizumab</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">）紧随其后，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2014</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">9</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">月获</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">FDA</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">批准，成为美国首个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">抑制剂。该药适用于晚期或转移性黑色素瘤，以及转移性非小细胞肺癌患者的治疗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">对于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">抑制剂，罗氏的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Atezolizumab</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">和阿斯利康的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Durvalumab</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">MEDI4736</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">）均已被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">FDA</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">授予突破性药物资格（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">BTD</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">）。二者治疗机制类似，适用于治疗转移性尿路上皮膀胱癌（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">UBC</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">）。通过靶向</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">蛋白，抑制其与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">T</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">细胞表面的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">B7-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">CD80</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">）受体结合，从而使</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">T</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">细胞激活，促进肿瘤免疫反应。而默克</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">辉瑞合作开发的抗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">药物</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\"> Avelumab </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">年下半年被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">FDA</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">授予孤儿药地位、快车道地位及突破性药物资格，并与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">12</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">月进入胃癌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">III</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">期临床开发。默克与辉瑞计划启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">个关键</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">III</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">期研究，调查</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Avelumab</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">治疗晚期或转移性胃</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">胃食管交界处（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">G/GEJ</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">）癌症的临床潜力。目前，国际巨头包括默克、罗氏、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">AZ</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">等针对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1/PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">治疗特定类型癌症，如肺癌、肾癌、乳腺癌、膀胱癌等已陆续展开相关研究。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: center; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: \'MS Mincho\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">国内</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">现</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: \'MS Mincho\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">状</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;\nfont-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#444444;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">年卫计委重大新药创制专项已将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">等列为重要靶点，国内越来越多的企业涉及这一领域。恒瑞医药的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">单抗进入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">CFDA</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">绿色通道；嘉和生物计划将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">药物与其它自有产品进行联合用药开发与申报。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">12</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">月，泰州君实生物医药科技有限公司申报的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">“</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">重组人源化抗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">单克隆抗体注射液</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">”</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">（受理号：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">CXSL1400138</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">）药物获批进入临床。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">2016</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">8</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">日，百济神州公司的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">BGB-A317</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">提已经顺利通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">FDA</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">的审评。该药物是一种针对免疫抑制性受体</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">的全人源单克隆抗体。这意味着针对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">BGB-A317</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">Ia/Ib</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">期临床试验可以在美国开展。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">针对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">的检测可以分为免疫组化检测和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">mRNA</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">检测。首度基因开发的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">mRNA</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">转录组检测项目，可一次性获得全部基因的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">mRNA</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">表达和融合情况，瞄准患病根源，缩短医生诊断时间，精准推荐用药，最大程度降低患者资金投入，延长生存期。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<!--EndFragment-->', '0', '2016-11-30 21:41:26', '2016-11-30 21:41:26');
