nor-latin;\n	mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n\n\n\n<!--StartFragment-->\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 9.75pt; text-indent: 24pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">日由全球癌症研究的权威机构</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">-</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">美国癌症研究学会（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">AACR</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">）举办的第三届“癌症研究新视野”大会在上海宝华万豪酒店隆重开幕，大会以“通过癌症科学寻找治愈方案”为主题，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">将重点介绍癌症研究各个重要领域最新和最振奋人心的研究成果，为来自全球各地的研究人员提供宝贵的交流机会，加强学术科研合作。此次会议将推动癌症科学和医学的发展，搭建富有活力的平台，帮助在国际层面上建立全新的合作关系。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 9.75pt; text-indent: 24pt;\"><img src=\"http://7xpsze.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/FgTvMIltp3ifltxeR5VP-7SQp6uy\" data-filename=\"AACR1.png\" style=\"width: 865px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 9.75pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16.5pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype\n id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\"\n path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\n <v:formulas>\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\n </v:formulas>\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"图片_x0020_0\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1028\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n alt=\"246041613495644886.jpg\" style=\'width:415pt;height:311pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square\'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:////Users/bian_ting/Library/Group%20Containers/UBF8T346G9.Office/msoclip1/01/clip_image001.jpg\"\n  o:title=\"246041613495644886.jpg\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><!--[endif]--></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 9.75pt; text-indent: 24pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">本次大会上，首度生物科技（苏州）有限公司携旗下尖端产品盛装亮相申城，以癌症基因检测技术为中心，通过提供“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FD-180</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">全药基因检测”、“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FD-600</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">全癌基因检测”、“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FD-Exome</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">全外显子健康检测”三款检测产品，为客户提供涵盖健康管理、精准用药、疗效跟踪等全方位个性化解决方案，吸引了众多国内外业内人士的咨询和交流。向行业专家及公众展示了首度基因应对癌症预后评价、精准用药、科研突破等挑战推出的最新成果，持续引领癌症基因检测领域的技术突破。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 9.75pt; text-indent: 24pt;\"><img src=\"http://7xpsze.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/Fg-2K-QnZf1bsNYA3WOYS6NMaVd2\" data-filename=\"AACR2.png\" style=\"width: 865px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top: 9.75pt; text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 16.5pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"图片_x0020_1\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1027\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"870104518212395825.jpg\" style=\'width:415pt;height:311pt;\n visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square\'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:////Users/bian_ting/Library/Group%20Containers/UBF8T346G9.Office/msoclip1/01/clip_image003.jpg\"\n  o:title=\"870104518212395825.jpg\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><!--[endif]--></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n\n</span><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">会议现场，首度基因展位始终保持着良好的人气，吸引了络绎不绝的参观体验人群，工作人员的热情服务也赢得了众多与会者们的一致好评。首度基因也将此次会议视为向外界展示我司高品质产品的最佳平台，现场举办了形式多样的客户活动，最高现场免费提供</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">8</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FD-Exome</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">全外显子健康检测名额，获得了来自国内外知名专家、行业领导及专业观众的盛赞。</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt;\"><img src=\"http://7xpsze.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/Fhcnb9SBcQwXTYJp6FzrdcFtY3Xg\" data-filename=\"AACR3.png\" style=\"width: 865px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"图片_x0020_2\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1026\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"910447724928411280.jpg\" style=\'width:415pt;height:311pt;\n visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square\'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:////Users/bian_ting/Library/Group%20Containers/UBF8T346G9.Office/msoclip1/01/clip_image005.jpg\"\n  o:title=\"910447724928411280.jpg\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><!--[endif]--></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">图为<span lang=\"EN-US\">FD-Exome</span>免费名额获奖者与工作人员合影</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"图片_x0020_3\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"17293742105455134.jpg\"\n style=\'width:416pt;height:554pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square\'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:////Users/bian_ting/Library/Group%20Containers/UBF8T346G9.Office/msoclip1/01/clip_image007.jpg\"\n  o:title=\"17293742105455134.jpg\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><!--[endif]--></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><img src=\"http://7xpsze.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/FpsxxyUXM8awqCU2lpgJEB8MkL0n\" data-filename=\"AACR4.png\" style=\"width: 865px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\'; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">图为<span lang=\"EN-US\">FD-Exome</span>免费名额获奖者与工作人员合影</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 24pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;此次展会，首度不仅向大众全面展示了成立一年多来沉淀和努力的硕果，更获得了一个跨地域交流合作的平台。未来，首度将继续加大在基因检测领域的投入研发，并希望与更多的企事业单位建立战略联盟，共同开展在基因大数据领域的合作研发，将基因序列信息转化为人类追求健康和战胜疾病的福音。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><br></span><!--EndFragment--></p>', '0', '2017-02-19 01:22:20', '2017-02-19 01:22:20');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('22', '0', '首度基因CEO唐元华受邀出席2016年百奥财富年会暨首届CEO高峰论坛', '', 'http://ac-9Liu9FBu.clouddn.com/14f3d2e51ffcadc5f836.jpeg', '<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:17.3pt;margin-left:\n0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;background:white;vertical-align:baseline;word-break:\nbreak-all\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\ncolor:#333333\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\ncolor:#333333\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>日下午，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span>年百奥财富年会暨首届<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>高峰论坛在上海西郊宾馆会议中心盛大开启，首度基因创始人兼<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>唐元华博士受邀出席本次论坛并发表了“引领中国走向生命信息化的新时代”的主题演讲。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 17.3pt; text-indent: 21pt; background-color: white; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://7xpsze.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/FqclFWaerDVKO-ajSXT3MkKm_Q51\" data-filename=\"图片 9.png\" style=\"width: 714px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\ncolor:#333333\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:17.3pt;margin-left:\n0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;background:white;vertical-align:baseline;word-break:\nbreak-all\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\n宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;\ncolor:#333333\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:17.3pt;margin-left:\n0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;background:white;\nvertical-align:baseline;word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\nmso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;color:#333333\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 唐元华博士首先代表全体公司同仁，对论坛的胜利召开表示了热烈祝贺，并感谢论坛组委会的盛情邀请。对于基因检测而言，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span>年注定要被写入历史铭记，唐元华博士兴奋的说，随着人类全基因组检测成本降到<span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span>美元以下，我们迎来了生命信息化时代这一新的历史机遇。基因大数据对于生命健康具有颠覆性意义，引领着人类从一刀切的对“症”用药步入到对“基因组”用药的精准医疗时代。在这一预估千亿市场量级的新兴行业背后，一场生命信息化时代的大健康变局蓬勃待发。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 17.3pt; background-color: white; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://7xpsze.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/FpiUdiPHG9l_jS5o_v9pnxGuxs4R\" data-filename=\"图片 10.png\" style=\"width: 658px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\nmso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;color:#333333\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:17.3pt;margin-left:\n0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;background:white;\nvertical-align:baseline;word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\nmso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;color:#333333\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:17.3pt;margin-left:\n0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;background:white;\nvertical-align:baseline;word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\nmso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;color:#333333\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 唐元华博士指出，凭借强大的海内外科研实力、专利技术和专家人才，历经一年多的积累与沉淀，首度基因已全面突破了基因测序、大数据分析、基因数据库三大技术壁垒，形成了疾病预防、肿瘤诊疗、科研服务三条产业链条，可为用户提供全方位的个性化解决方案。未来首度基因将打造国内权威的基因信息数据库，为每一位国民提供基因组信息服务，将基因组学转化成人类战胜疾病的福音。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 17.3pt; background-color: white; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"http://7xpsze.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/FsICtQQVzs-lYEHT8J5WkJiU_0b-\" data-filename=\"图片 11.png\" style=\"width: 672px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\nmso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;color:#333333\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:17.3pt;margin-left:\n0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;background:white;\nvertical-align:baseline;word-break:break-all\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\nmso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;color:#333333\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:17.3pt;margin-left:\n0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;background:white;vertical-align:baseline;word-break:\nbreak-all\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-hans