14px;\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">转移性非小细胞肺癌，对克唑替尼耐药或不能耐受患者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 60pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PD-1</span><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">Nivolumab</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Opdovo</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">转移性鳞状非小细胞肺癌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 60pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PD-1</span><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">Pembrolizumab</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Keytruda</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">表达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PD-L1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">的转移性非小细胞肺癌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 60pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">VEGF</span><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">贝伐珠单抗（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Avastin</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">联合卡铂、紫杉醇治疗局部晚期或复发性非鳞状非小细胞肺癌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 60pt;\"><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">VEGFR2</span><o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td style=\"padding: 0cm; height: 60pt;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">雷莫芦单抗（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Cyramza</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span>